Dana  Ruzicka 
Executive Compensation
As Vice President and Chief Product Officer at AVID TECHNOLOGY INC, Dana  Ruzicka  made $699,578 in total compensation.  Of this total $278,923 was received as a salary, $94,381 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $319,719 was awarded as stock and $6,555 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


